  <entry>
    <title>git-helper</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2016/08/10/git-helper/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2016/08/10/git-helper/</id>
    <published>2016-08-10T10:01:03.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-08-10T10:06:21.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote class="blockquote-center">git设置，操作命令</blockquote>

<ul>
<li><a href="#settings">设置</a></li>
<li><a href="#operation">操作命令</a></li>
</ul>
<p></p><h2 id="settings">设置</h2><br>1.使用系统存储的密码<p></p>
<blockquote>
<p>git config –global credential.helper osxkeychain</p>
</blockquote>
<p>2.使用默认diff工具</p>
<blockquote>
<p>git config –global merge.tool opendiff</p>
</blockquote>
<p>3.查看已有配置信息</p>
<blockquote>
<p>git config –list</p>
</blockquote>
<p>4.全局配置信息文件</p>
<blockquote>
<p>~/.gitconfig</p>
</blockquote>
<p>5.开读写权限</p>
<blockquote>
<p>chmod 600 ~/.ssh/config</p>
</blockquote>
<p></p><h2 id="operation">操作命令</h2><br>1.撤销commit<p></p>
<blockquote>
<p>git reset –hard <sha1-commit-id></sha1-commit-id></p>
</blockquote>
<p>2.恢复某个commit</p>
<blockquote>
<p>git cherry-pick <sha1-commit-id></sha1-commit-id></p>
</blockquote>
<p>3.删除所有本地修改</p>
<blockquote>
<p>git reset –hard</p>
</blockquote>
<p>4.删除所有本地添加的文件，文件夹</p>
<blockquote>
<p>git clean -f</p>
</blockquote>
<p>5.删除所线上有tag</p>
<blockquote>
<p>git tag -l | xargs git push origin –delete</p>
</blockquote>
<p>6.删除本地所有tag</p>
<blockquote>
<p>git tag -l | xargs git tag -d</p>
</blockquote>
<p>7.切换远程branch</p>
<blockquote>
<p>git checkout –track origin/dev.sp1</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;blockquote class=&quot;blockquote-center&quot;&gt;git设置，操作命令&lt;/blockquote&gt;

